                        <note xml:id="Ruth-004-fn2" type="footnote">Spelled the same way as in
                            Hebrew original: <foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;"
                                >שַׂלְמָה</foreign>
                             . Cf. next verse: <foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;"
                                >שַׂלְמֹון</foreign>
                             .</note>
                        <note xml:id="Ruth-004-fn3" type="footnote">Heb. ‘Finished’.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Ruth-004-fn4" type="footnote">Heb. ‘And this is the end of the
                            Scroll of Ruth. Glory to the one who led us from slavery to
                            freedom’.</note>
